 {"id":"brenner_bot-hog","title":"Build crosswalk comparison table component","description":"# Task

Create the interactive crosswalk table showing concept mappings across all three models.

# The Table

From README:
| Concept | Opus | GPT | Gemini |
|---------|------|-----|--------|
| Foundation | Two Axioms | One sentence + objective function | Root Access |
| Operators | Operator algebra + compositions | Operator basis + loop + rubric | Instruction set |
| Execution | Brenner Loop | 9-step loop + worksheet | Debug protocol + scheduler |
| Quality | Failure modes section | 12 guardrails | Error handling |
| Social | Conversation as technology | Conversation as hypothesis search | Brenner-Crick GAN |

